{"tid":2334923,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂外賣煲仔飯飯焦勁黑　網民狠批：似飯炭多過飯焦！","createTime":"2020-12-21T12:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:50:32.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9b85080065270b8cb398257b1aedf4e4a27eba7","tid":2334923,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"最近天氣轉凍，不少市民都去吃熱辣辣的煲仔飯暖胃。不過有網民聲稱大家樂的煲仔飯竟現出大片焦黑飯焦，更「有圖有真相」，事件引起網民熱議。《香港01》飲食記者整理網民留言，並就此事向大家樂查詢，惟截稿前仍未收到大家樂回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201221/417656024275619840765280.jpeg/gbLdKBDIA39w8wRIPZYC8CJKeM6hYIaTpKIVZqSiFWY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201221%2F417656024275619840765280.jpeg%2FgbLdKBDIA39w8wRIPZYC8CJKeM6hYIaTpKIVZqSiFWY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=24eb7bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前有網民在facebook群組「中伏飲食報料區」發圖文，聲稱光顧大家樂元朗形點分店，發現煲仔飯的飯焦完全焦黑一片，並非正常的金黃色飯焦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201221/417656029967552512456021.jpeg/SIm1HtwM0UKsuIszG_BKowE-Tacu26d-M6wMjjOsDI4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201221%2F417656029967552512456021.jpeg%2FSIm1HtwM0UKsuIszG_BKowE-Tacu26d-M6wMjjOsDI4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dd1cc0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201221/417656029967552512456021.jpeg/SIm1HtwM0UKsuIszG_BKowE-Tacu26d-M6wMjjOsDI4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201221%2F417656029967552512456021.jpeg%2FSIm1HtwM0UKsuIszG_BKowE-Tacu26d-M6wMjjOsDI4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dd1cc0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中所見煲仔飯的飯焦被燒燶，非常焦黑。（網民曾熙堯圖片）<br />\n<br />\n帖文引發熱議，不少網民都在帖文下留言，其中不少網民mean爆留言，「似飯炭多過飯焦」，有人就搞笑地指有「飯焦」才香口，「食煲仔飯就梗係要有飯焦㗎啦～」。"},{"pid":"facb35174cc8357607b29b0df5e5794ceb3a030e","tid":2334923,"uid":322965,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:46:11.000Z","msg":"食籃店抵死la"},{"pid":"d9cdc9a93c984b9fa73b9e827a77a891c77a7e70","tid":2334923,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"食藍店送致癌物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2842456ee0995e9115760943d798fd8238be959","tid":2334923,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？"}]}